{
  "stem": "12674.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took a bunch of us girls, and they sent us to a agricultural camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Actually, it was a big farm, and they-- you took one of the barns, and they made a-- a girls' camp out of it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They put some beds in there, some iron bedsteads and straw sacks, and that's-- that was our home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were about 30-- some 30-some-odd girls, 32, something like that, all Jewish girls between 14 and 16, or between 13 and 16, really.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wasn't one of the youngest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were sent to this place in Silesia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It-- it is not important.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was in a-- it was-- it was in a county which was called Gardelegen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Gardelegen became a very well-known concentration camp later on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I don't think it had any connection to that farm where we were sitting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a place called [NON-ENGLISH], [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Kreis ?] Gardelegen. 'Kreis' is the equivalent of 'county' in English.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it was a small agricultural thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wasn't really in a village.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were on a farm out in the middle of nowhere in this barn.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were-- we were harvesting asparagus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, asparagus grows very funny.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It grows in-- in furrows like little, I don't know, little mountains or sort of rows, which are approximately less than a foot high.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they're little hills that go along for [? ends. ?] And you get a knife, which looks like a chisel with a bent sort of a thing and has a-- has a knife at the bottom.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And asparagus, when it comes-- at that time in Austria, in-- in-- in Germany, asparagus had to be white.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
